                <div class="card-thumb"><img src="https://img.gamedistribution.com/644044c3831d4d77a6cee53e6b9d01c9-512x512.jpeg" alt="Fruit Swipe" loading="lazy" onerror="this.src='https://picsum.photos/seed/fruitswipe14/400/225'"><div class="card-badge badge-new">✨ New</div><div class="card-overlay"><div class="play-btn-overlay"><i class="fas fa-play"></i> Play Now</div></div></div>
                <div class="card-body"><div class="card-meta"><span class="card-genre">Casual</span><span class="card-rating"><i class="fas fa-star"></i> 4.5</span></div><h3 class="card-title">Fruit Swipe</h3><p class="card-desc">Swipe to slice and match juicy fruits. Fast reactions win the day!</p><div class="card-footer"><span class="card-players"><i class="fas fa-circle"></i> 2.7k playing</span><button class="btn-play"><i class="fas fa-play"></i> Play</button></div></div>
            </div>
